			<div class="content" id="post-content-2829254">
									

<p>I guess so, but infohazards to my mind are a bit more&#8230; automatic, I guess? Like I never got that writing about it specifically is what triggered it, rather that it was just looking out specifically for it being mentioned to find people to talk to whereas infohazards wouldn't chose to respond, they just &quot;happen&quot;. Maybe an irrelevant distinction.</p>

